thread.title: Vicki Lynn

author: Vicki Lynn
title: Vicki Lynn
text: I received a gift basket at Christmas time that included a small box of something called CoffeeGo! It's a coffee-flavored candy that I immediately became addicted to. This was one of the few sites that I could find that carries this fun little item. I laughed when I realized I had to buy it in a five-pound box but...a girl's gotta do what a girl's gotta do! The ordering process was easy and my order arrived on time. I'm now responsibly enjoying my little coffee treat.
